phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common testing mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No setup | Use @Before |
| No error tests | Test errors |
| No mocks | Use MockK |
| No coroutine support | Use runTest |
| No cleanup | Use @After |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use setup
@Before
fun setup() {
    viewModel = PlayerViewModel()
}

// 2. Test errors
@Test
fun testError() {
    // Test error case
}

// 3. Use mocks
repository = mockk()

// 4. Use runTest
@Test
fun testCoroutine() = runTest {
    // Test code
}

// 5. Cleanup
@After
fun cleanup() {
    // Cleanup code
}

// 6. Use assertions
assertThat(result).isEqualTo(expected)
```
